<a href="/akira/dtd/4049-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4049">Move the United Nations to Jerusalem&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8469-4049">longshot9999</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">1 day ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The title is only half of this idea, the other half would be for countries to unite together and push for Jerusalem to be declared a World Heritage site.  In order to keep the various religious sects who claim pieces of it from fighting one another the administrators of this World Heritage site would come from other religions that have no claim on the area (Buddhism, Shintoism, etc...)</div>
