<div id="Idea_4047"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4047-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4047">Help Israel Help the Palestinians&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8469-4049">longshot9999</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">1 day ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">For the last several years Israel has been the top recepient of our foreign aid.  This idea wouldn't change that.  In fact, it would encourage us to increase the amount of that aid.  There would be one new condition attached to this aid though - Israel would have to use fifty percent of it to help the Palestinians.  The aid would be offerred on a take-it-or-leave-it basis, and each following year's aid would be dependent on Israel showing it had actually spent the Palestinians portion on the Palestinians. </div>
